Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擋住去路的巨大牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換個角度想就是一扇巨門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帥呆的飛車特技演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在超炫的場面背後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隱藏著不為人知的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一看清真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是外表看似小孩 頭腦聰明過人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的名字就是《名偵探柯南》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假面超人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.95,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跑不掉的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你逃得了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假...假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.86,0:03:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.37,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汽車特技的極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對...絕對不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個計畫是絕不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太危險了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為是在和誰說話啊？都給我閉嘴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個的確危險，那是對其他的特技演員來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.55,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我就沒問題，這種特技已經做到不想再做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對，木島啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.72,0:04:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...是啊...只不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬別把鏡頭切囉，木島，不要呼嚨我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裡衝進去到墜樓為止，不換鏡一氣荷成！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.97,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是從下面拍的話你從車裡跳出去是沒問題，但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力石先生...現在的你...已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs30}{\pos(325,40)}今天真太感謝你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.74,0:04:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這可以看到假面超人的摩托車，真是太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人面還真是大咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是人面很廣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！我還拿到了很多假面超人的貼紙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不拿的人就太傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼？已經什麼已經？說清楚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎了怎了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在吵什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵架了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在都用數位方式作特技\n比傳純的表演更驚心動迫，想得到的都作得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後就不再需要這種落後的特技了，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...也不是這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.02,0:05:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪人開的汽車一直到樓頂，換成另一部一樣的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設原來那部車叫作Ａ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一部要換的車是遙控車叫作Ｂ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替原來怪人開的Ａ車由Ｂ車繼續衝出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然攝影機是由下往上拍並沒有換車的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再...用電腦數位剪接一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來特技的效果就十分逼真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向盤正常，剎車也正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...就這樣子了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點決定一下，準備好了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這邊也準備好了嗎？木島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你一副沒什麼把握的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再吵下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.77,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製作人已經同意了，就照這個計畫開拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好囉...你會後悔的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs30}{\pos(325,40)}你快給我放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.97,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假面迴旋踢那個咻咻的樣子太帥了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咻咻的樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.37,0:06:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在先休息吃飯，準備拍下一個鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請大家先做好準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得那個人不是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正最後都會被假面超人打敗啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想得可真好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.66,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂...只不過是電視劇裡的故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.20,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是真無聊呢...好不容易來這卻沒看到拍攝實況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是午休也沒辦法嘛...元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們要不要也去吃午飯呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人沒有拿到便當？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子咕嚕叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元太你真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急得沒話說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼簽不知道可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯！謝謝你喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？元太和光彥人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.54,0:07:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太讚了！連車牌都一模一樣咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩部車應該就是在樓頂交換的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中一輛用遙控器控制從樓頂墜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得很刺激呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來作個紀念，鏘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元太不行啦！你在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有在作什麼啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先走一步...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你囉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你開什麼玩笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你來插什麼嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.37,0:09:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是插嘴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人又吵架啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果拍攝能順利進行的話就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總讓人耽心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力石先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？已經開始了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰...誰快去阻止他啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打算要按自己的計畫去做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力...力石先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎...怎會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說...我才不要你這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.74,0:10:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底發生什麼事情了？是怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全帶並沒有被解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.12,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要從樓頂衝破柵欄前，想從位座跳出來但失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是個意外嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是...有可能是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攝影師叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.74,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才攝影機全都拍下來了吧？可不可以借我看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊我也要確定一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裡呀？他又自己去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂...你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼回事，柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不意外事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是巧妙醞釀時機的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.29,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死者是三十八歲的替身特技演員力石健吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.71,0:12:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來死因是掉下來時...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.90,0:12:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，車子撞擊到地面時造成其全身內傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓汽車從那麼高的地方墜落下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣拍攝真是太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣子，我們不會讓他做那種特技的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.89,0:13:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為力石他自己堅持要做他自己想做的特技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確的說法...不是特技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是正式開拍前的掃興節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.71,0:13:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂為什麼力石先生要這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他急於求成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.07,0:13:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急於求成？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.99,0:13:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.86,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也不是不知，年輕的特技演員日新月異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.39,0:13:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也早就厭倦了傳統拍攝技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是說不需要特技演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這種電視劇還是絕對少不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在電腦特效的幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來一些特技都不用冒生命危險去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.26,0:13:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以也確實是有因此而被解雇的特技演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我說也沒用，是製作人負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那位製作人在退休後...把位子要給你來坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好囉...你會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快給我放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.51,0:13:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保住自己的飯碗所以就急於求成去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木島您說得好像自己很瞭解他心思一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最耽心遭到製片人解雇的人應該是你才對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.83,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底私下做了什麼，力石他好像知道一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別胡說八道！再說我又沒對他做什麼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醜聞被人揭穿又被他揍了的人不就是你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.11,0:14:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快住手，在這種情況下請你們不要吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來...你好像也常常被他扁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.64,0:14:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還說過想殺了他的話不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是想賴說是我去把他殺了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.61,0:14:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警官，請你們盡快事實還原吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一件意外事故吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這件事是不是由於汽車保養不良所造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要請專門負責鑒識的人來仔細調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是絕不可能，我們保養沒有疏乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你有動機啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你也不是一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.02,0:15:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過現階段看來應該是意外的可能性比較高一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是理所當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士，我們來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是偽裝成意外的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...有什麼證據？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一個確定的因素是被害人力石先生的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性格嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如這個特技難度越高他就越想親自表現一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前他就曾去特地找這樣子的機會向下跳咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是職業病吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然如果要做的話我們會做好萬全的準備和排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要做得好，效果可以堪稱一流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力石先生呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.35,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是一流...是他年輕時的確能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但最近他的水準降低也是看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果犯人利用了他的這個特性呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這話是怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.21,0:16:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深町先生，當時力石先生對你說了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣，我一定要你看我真正的特技本領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣，根本不聽勸告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正好相反！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相反？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 並不是力石先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是你深町先生，是你先開口的，像是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你們在立場上互相反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在表演的順序上可能還是互相接納的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是就唆使他做了些什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡...說八道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你的意思就是我殺了他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.98,0:16:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，犯人就是你...深町先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.15,0:16:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿笠先生...即使他是教唆了力石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但實際上駕駛並墜落的卻是力石自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人並不能成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，正因為如此，深町先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.31,0:17:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可能就對力石說了這樣的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在Ａ車裡並沒有裝置準備墜落爆炸的炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.58,0:17:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以開Ａ車的話這些特技沒意義，絕對不要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一說力石反而下定了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦到了屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.62,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就迅速換上裝有炸藥的Ｂ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.24,0:17:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並作出在墜落的瞬間逃出去的極危險特技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們大家看看他的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說在屋頂上停放著的是Ｂ車嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.44,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，這輛車裡並沒有裝置炸藥，是Ａ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎樣？越來越糊塗了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.78,0:17:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，等一下喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高木，慎重起見你去屋頂查查那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.69,0:18:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官，找到了，果然這裡的是Ｂ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.45,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說力石先生並沒有從Ａ車換到Ｖ車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.68,0:18:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是直接進行特技表演了，最後失敗而墜落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要那麼著急下結論啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們能不能回憶意外剛發生後的力石先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.59,0:18:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有鑒識科所拍攝的照片的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然就是這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.89,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元太貼上去的假面超人貼紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是貼在負責車輛的叔叔開到屋頂上的行李箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，元太？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.34,0:18:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一定不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.07,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他果然是在屋頂上換了車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歹...歹勢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.84,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我兩台車都有貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都貼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.77,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說證明不了他是否曾經換車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倒未必，我要你們看的是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...攝影的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能再讓我們看一次你剛剛拍的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，門逢並沒有夾到東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.56,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之後並沒有跡象表示他在屋頂開門或關門過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那炸藥呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛...只要在事先換好就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就以這點來說，換了車的證據是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.24,0:19:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當時立刻就上屋頂去看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.64,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車頭還是熱的，就好像是引擎剛剛才熄火一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦...那麼說果然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太荒謬！就算是這樣又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.61,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設，假設而已呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.30,0:19:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是我唆使他讓他在屋頂上換車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在車墜落之前沒有成功跳出來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.95,0:19:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼說也都是他本人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說他的反應力變差了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.73,0:20:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在跳車的前一刻，如果有踩剎車就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連這一點都做不到的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，跳出來還是踩剎車也好這本來就都是不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這話很難瞭解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你們能回想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該停在屋頂的Ｂ車是輛什麼車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.73,0:20:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它除了有裝上墜落時的炸藥以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遙控嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遙控器現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...他說要看這個遙控好不好操作我就拿給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了它之後，就可以知道誰是Ａ誰是Ｂ車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在哭泣一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我借了很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此不自覺地盜用了作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.77,0:21:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事被他發現了就威脅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.46,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是你就反過來利用力石的性格設計了殺人計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.80,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你計算力石先生開的Ａ車到達屋頂換到Ｂ車的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.25,0:21:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用遙控器將車發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.06,0:21:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剎車失靈、門也打不開，就這樣把車子開下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後力石先生被認定死因是技巧失誤造成的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家認為嚴重破壞的是Ａ車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.09,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再若無其事將遙控器還給管車輛的西協先生就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是這樣想的，對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃不下了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假面超人太帥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.27,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元太...你不能這樣子貼得到處都是貼紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.13,0:23:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的推理也都喪失能力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.65,0:23:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是夠了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山本他自殺了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定還另有隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.89,0:24:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一些我沒發現的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.31,0:24:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.90,0:24:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨終的安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.86,0:24:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集柯南提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.16,0:24:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攪拌棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.46,0:24:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就憑一根攪拌棒能解開整個案件嗎？
